N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 316.1 - Authorization required to make devices bearing official marks

State Regulations

No brand manufacturer, printer or other person shall
cast, print, lithograph, or otherwise make or cause to be made any device
containing any official mark or simulation thereof without prior written
authority therefor from the commissioner as provided for in Part 317 of this

Article. Notes
